OL,3,CSomerset couple who lost thousands in
OL,4,CPost Office scandal reject apology
OL,6,FA couple from Somerset who lost
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds of their own money
OL,8,Fwhile running a branch of the Post
OL,9,FOffice have said an apology from the
OL,10,Fcompany's boss is "too little, too
OL,11,Flate".
OL,13,FAndrew and Kathy Tizzard ran their
OL,14,Fbranch in South Wales but ended up
OL,15,Fusing their own money to make up for a
OL,16,F#20,000 shortfall caused by the new
OL,17,FHorizon IT accounting software.
