OL,6,FThe-then boss of the Post Office,
OL,7,FPaula Vennels, broke down in tears
OL,8,Fwhile giving evidence to an inquiry
OL,9,Finvestigating the Horizon IT scandal
OL,10,Ffor the first time on Wednesday 22 May.
OL,12,FPaula said: "I fully accept now, that
OL,13,Fthe Post Office knew that. I
OL,14,Fcompletely accept it. Personally, I
OL,15,Fdidn't know that and I'm incredibly
OL,16,Fsorry."
OL,18,FBut Mr and Mrs Tizzard criticised Ms
OL,19,FVennels apology, as "hollow" and "too
OL,20,Flittle, too late".
