OL,6,F"Well to be honest with you, it's just
OL,7,Fhollow," Kathy said.
OL,9,F"We can all sit there after the event
OL,10,Fand say 'I'm sorry for this' or 'I'm
OL,11,Fsorry for that'. But in reality, I
OL,12,Fpersonally feel she knew an awful lot
OL,13,Fof what was going on.
OL,15,FAndrew added: "It's too little, too
OL,16,Flate. We need the questions answered."
OL,18,FThe pair were visited by investigators
OL,19,Fdemanding to see their accounts, as
OL,20,Fportrayed in the ITV drama Mr Bates
OL,21,Fversus the Post Office.
