OL,6,FThe only way the couple could avoid
OL,7,Ffurther action was to pay back the
OL,8,Fmoney - which they were wrongly
OL,9,Faccused of taking - themselves. This
OL,10,Famounted to around #20,000 and they
OL,11,Fhave never been compensated for it.
OL,13,FAndrew recalled: "Balance nights, we
OL,14,Fwere there until two in the morning,
OL,15,Fstaring at Horizon, not understanding
OL,16,Fhow we could remove errors that we
OL,17,Fknew were not there."
