OL,6,FBut for Kathy, the impact was even
OL,7,Fmore severe and she was admitted to an
OL,8,Fintensive care unit in hospital for
OL,9,Forgan failure, due to stress.
OL,11,F"My weight had dropped so much because
OL,12,Fof the stress", Kathy said.
OL,14,F"I also remember saying to the
OL,15,Fspecialist - when he said ' I think
OL,16,Fyou're going to be okay to go home and
OL,17,Fgo back in a couple of days' - I said
OL,18,F'please don't send me back'."
