OL,6,FThe experience still affects this
OL,7,Fcouple, having received no
OL,8,Fcompensation and the pair know they
OL,9,Fare not alone.
OL,11,FKathy and Andrew say they finally want
OL,12,Fthe truth - and for those responsible
OL,13,Fto be held to account.
